# Rust build output
/target/

# Coverage
*.profraw
*.profdata
coverage-summary.txt
lcov.info

# Key material — the beacon's private signing key MUST NEVER be committed. It lives ONLY
# in the `BEACON_SIGNING_KEY` GitHub Actions secret. Ignore every private-key shape so an
# accidental local key export can never be staged. (The PUBLIC key keys/beacon-root.pub is
# tracked deliberately and is not matched by these patterns.)
*.pem
!keys/beacon-root.pub
*.key
*_ed25519
*_ed25519.*
id_ed25519*
secret-key*
signing-key*
beacon-signing*
*.priv

# Node (commitlint tooling if ever run locally)
node_modules/

# Misc
*.log
.env
.DS_Store
dist/
